---
title: BBQ Prawns & Slaw Tacos with Cheddar Cheese & Plant-Based Mayo
description: It’s a good day when you’re having tacos for dinner. Let’s pack these tortillas with as many All-American spiced prawns as
possible, tossed with baby spinach and a colourful slaw on top. Don’t forget the Cheddar cheese!
